            <div>Participant authorizes Intrax and its representatives to seek medical attention on behalf of the Participant in the event of sickness, accident or other emergency during the Program. Participant also authorizes any physician to release any information acquired in the course of examination or treatment. This authorization shall be valid for the entire duration of the Intrax Program. Participant is financially responsible for any medical treatment received which is not covered by the provided accident and sickness insurance.</div>
