      <h2 class="pgbr-bf">6) Payment Policies</h2>
      <ul class="lower-latin">
        <li>Prices are subject to adjustment due to circumstances beyond the control of Intrax, including but not limited to lack of participation and currency exchange rate fluctuations.</li>
        <li>Program fees are due according to the following schedule:
        <p>&nbsp;</p>
        <table>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Application Fee</strong></td>
            <td>Due within seven (7) calendar days of acceptance to program. </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td><strong>Final Payment</strong></td>
