      <ul class="lower-latin">
        <li>Neither the Host Company nor Intrax bears any liability for any losses or claims incurred by a Participant in connection with dismissal, early withdrawal or the Host Company or Intrax's termination of the Program.
        </li>
        <li>If a Participant withdraws from the Program for any reason before the confirmation of a match to an internship with a Host Company, Intrax will retain the non-refundable Application Fee.</li>
        <li>If a Participant withdraws from the Program for any reason after confirmation of a match with an internship with a Host Company, Intrax will retain the non-refundable Application Fee and the percentage of Program Fees according to the schedule below:
         <div class="nested-list lower-roman">
            <div>90-76 days prior to start date- 50% of Program Fees.</div>
            <div>75-61 days prior to start date - 75% of Program Fees.</div>
           <div>60 days or less prior to start date - 100 % of Program Fees.</div>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li>Participant will not be eligible for a refund if:
          <div class="nested-list lower-roman">
            <div>Participant withdraws from the Program after the start of the Program for any reason, or</div>
            <div>Participant is dismissed for any reason, or</div>
            <div>Intrax per its sole discretion dismisses Participant for not having fulfilled all Program requirements (including but not limited to: payment in full of the Program Fees; submission of all signed forms and documents; successful completion of necessary visa requirements).</div>
         </div>
        </li>
        <li>In case of visa denial, Participant will be eligible for following refund:
          <div class="nested-list lower-roman">
            <div>Program fee</div>
            <div>Placement fee minus $500 (if candidate had accepted an Intrax arranged position)</div>
         </div>
        </li>
        <li>In case of visa denial, Participant will not be eligible for following refund:
          <div class="nested-list lower-roman">
            <div>Non-refundable application fee</div>
            <div>SEVIS fee</div>
